description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Medical Recruitment Administrator&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Medical Staffing team. We are seeking to recruit an enthusiastic and flexible person to deliver an efficient and effective recruitment and retention service for medical staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To provide comprehensive support to the Medical Staffing Team including the Recruitment and Advisory functions. Ensuring a positive and professional image of the organisation is maintained with stakeholders and all contacts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be expected to have excellent organisational and communication skills and be able to prioritise their workload, demonstrate the ability to work under pressure. A good knowledge of Microsoft applications including Word, Excel, and databases is also essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please read the job description and person specification for more information&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 11th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Planned Interview Date: tbc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Michele Wilkinson, Medical Staffing Manager on 01865 222084 michele.wilkinson@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kirstie Lowe, Medical Staffing Supervisor, Kirstie.lowe@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
